      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the chicken is in the oven, combine the <strong>green tomato chutney</strong> with the <strong>remaining natural yoghurt </strong>in a medium bowl</p><p>Add a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a large pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> – this is your<strong> slaw sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
